286
00:21:36,890 --> 00:21:39,150
Ouch, brother!

287
00:21:39,150 --> 00:21:40,550
Come on, everybody!

288
00:21:41,010 --> 00:21:41,940
Hurry up!

289
00:21:44,440 --> 00:21:45,570
Don't kick me!

290
00:21:45,570 --> 00:21:46,610
Ouch!

291
00:21:46,610 --> 00:21:50,680
The Black Foot brother is gonna
kill us before the deadly gas does!

292
00:21:51,530 --> 00:21:52,810
Don't be a baby!

293
00:21:52,810 --> 00:21:54,000
He's crazy!

294
00:21:54,890 --> 00:21:56,890
Hurry up!

295
00:21:56,890 --> 00:21:58,730
If you wanna save the children,

296
00:21:58,730 --> 00:22:00,420
go to the Biscuit Room now!

297
00:22:00,540 --> 00:22:04,340
B BUILDING 3RD FLOOR - THE BISCUIT ROOM

298
00:22:08,130 --> 00:22:11,200
