305
00:22:21,770 --> 00:22:23,770
Wait, Mocha!

306
00:22:23,770 --> 00:22:25,680
Give us the candy!

307
00:22:25,680 --> 00:22:27,650
No! You all have to
come to your senses!

308
00:22:28,710 --> 00:22:30,720
You can't have it all to yourself!

309
00:22:30,720 --> 00:22:31,780
Stop running!

310
00:22:33,030 --> 00:22:34,740
