escape, despite the relentless attacks.

322
00:23:32,720 --> 00:23:35,890
It's then that Monet transforms
into a terrifying monster

323
00:23:35,890 --> 00:23:37,260
and the situation worsens.

324
00:23:37,260 --> 00:23:39,980
The crew find themselves backed into a corner.

325
00:23:39,980 --> 00:23:41,450
On the next episode of One Piece!

326
00:23:41,450 --> 00:23:44,690
"A Deadly Fight in a Blizzard!
